title: Lee Konitz Talks About His February 19 Iowa Concert
description: KFMG Radio's John Busbee interviews alto saxophonist Lee Konitz about his upcoming duo performance with pianist Dan Tepfer scheduled for February 19 at Caspe Terrace in Waukee, Iowa.
